Known issues:
- The MAC address is not fixed (this should probably be fixed in barebox).
- Sometimes the camera OV5640 is not detected by the I2C-bus. Rebooting
  the system solves the problem.
- HDMI dispaly is not hotplug detected, i.e. works as Coldplug only.
